---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FormattedDate from "../components/FormattedDate.astro";
import { Calendar, User, ArrowLeft, Smile } from "@lucide/astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

const title = "About Me";
const description = "A developer who commits like it's a heartbeat.";
const pubDate = new Date("2025-05-09");
const heroImage = "/img/about-me.png";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} maxWidth="max-w-6xl">
  <article class="py-10 px-4 sm:px-6">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <header class="mb-12">
      <!-- Back to home link -->
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-md text-base font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors no-underline mb-8"
      >
        <ArrowLeft class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" />
        Back to home
      </a>

      <!-- Page metadata -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 mb-5 text-base text-gray-600"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <Calendar class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />
          <FormattedDate date={pubDate} />
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <User class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />
          <span>Personal</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Page title -->
      <h1
        class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6"
      >
        {title}
      </h1>

      <!-- Subtitle/Description -->
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 italic mb-8">
        {description}
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Image -->
    {
      heroImage && (
        <div class="mb-12 overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <Image
            width={1200}
            height={600}
            src={heroImage || "/placeholder.png"}
            alt="About me"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      )
    }

    <!-- Content -->
    <div
      class="format format-lg md:format-xl max-w-none format-headings:font-bold format-headings:text-gray-900 format-p:text-gray-700 format-a:text-blue-600 format-a:no-underline hover:format-a:underline format-img:rounded-lg"
    >
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        With the rise of Large Language Models, I find myself locked in a
        parental power struggle with digital offspring who know everything but
        understand nothing. "Why, GPT, would you nest ternary operators inside a
        switch case? Why." I argue, they respond, I sigh, we continue.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        I'm looking to build. To explore. To ship questionable features at 2AM
        and then refactor them at 2:03AM. I am the IT Alienâ„¢. I bring commits.
        I bring lint. You bring... snacks?
      </p>

      <!-- Fun Fact Section -->
      <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Fun Facts</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Did you know? The average developer spends 30% of their time debugging
          code they wrote while sleep-deprived. The other 70% is spent wondering
          why their code works at all.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <button
            class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-md bg-black !text-white hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors no-underline"
          >
            <Smile class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />
            Generate fun fact
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
